..只望脫離搵咁小錢既行列<br />\n屌我做左兩年幾野  得果皮半   日日都好唔開心"},{"pid":"4448778a83e200fe80153740ac0b7414b9f252d8","tid":520784,"uid":88190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"同意，有10個浪費人生既因素，亦有啲因素係燃燒緊人生<br />\n1.唔健康既習慣<br />\n吸煙唔長氣講，夜瞓真係好出事，冇精神 又易病 有福都冇命享<br />\n2.賭／先洗未來錢<br />\n老實講，人生好多都同錢有關，欠債真係慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c12b885f629dfce82b2df59b8388186f88cc68","tid":520784,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"好彩未睇呢篇野之前都有覺悟<br />\n搵到自己喜歡既興趣/工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲仲會讀書"},{"pid":"757ee5fea597fc561a462d0e61f0d54f3801909a","tid":520784,"uid":31007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇篇嘢之前已經發現咗，奈何之前真係浪費人生，但依家有改善、會行動追求目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608b6ac645728c3a21eb994f8aa7196105e4dac","tid":520784,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4448778a83e200fe80153740ac0b7414b9f252d8","tid":520784,"uid":88190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"同意，有10個浪費人生既因素，亦有啲因素係燃燒緊人生<br />\n1.唔健康既習慣<br />\n吸煙唔長氣講，夜瞓真係好出事，冇精神 又易病 有福都冇命享<br />\n2.賭／先洗未來錢<br />\n老實講，人生好多都同錢有關，欠債真係慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"中晒喎 仲要成日打j"},{"pid":"81bae5b127197d81814c35e6435270016a071d91","tid":520784,"uid":137747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:20:17.000Z","msg":"中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7366f33a3a6d71cb28e759489ef0379bfe5f0c26","tid":520784,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"我都唔想咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e3ce42f7fe3ad7403debdac509451b93547b08","tid":520784,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504a9b8d0f0d8976cdb1e1273df6f771286cd363","tid":520784,"uid":28908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"中左兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多野你睇人好人睇你好 人地付出左好多努力先搵返成果 人地會羨慕你放假訓緊教玩緊輕輕鬆鬆生活"},{"pid":"e53af5717823330416c673f9f1aa147f525aa618","tid":520784,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中左兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多野你睇人好人睇你好 人地付出左好多努力先搵返成果 人地會羨慕你放假訓緊教玩緊輕輕鬆鬆生活</blockquote><br />\n懶散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc907efb07caf5859b12f148113dab95e702cef","tid":520784,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e53af5717823330416c673f9f1aa147f525aa618","tid":520784,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中左兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多野你睇人好人睇你好 人地付出左好多努力先搵返成果 人地會羨慕你放假訓緊教玩緊輕輕鬆鬆生活</blockquote><br />\n懶散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"今日又夜訓啦屌"},{"pid":"ddfaf676643adabbb97d9ad9198b3d61cbd5b29b","tid":520784,"uid":43055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"中哂10樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明自己唔甘心咁就一世<br />\n但又冇動力去變<br />\n日日鳩下鳩下就過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79147be15f4326a63759ddeb5f102823b6637c81","tid":520784,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"其實老實講，好多人所謂夢想同錢同成就係掛勾。咁已經係錯。<br />\n當然錢好重要。但當錢係會影響你對件事嘅熱愛，咁你已經唔洗講咩努力，因為個樣嘅根本唔係你夢想。除非你夢想就係億萬富豪。<br />\n而事實上大部份人係從心而發地冇熱愛冇夢想，點講都冇用。再者就係社會上未出現有相關嘅職業令佢熱愛。例如Youtuber都係呢十年先有。<br />\n我係咁睇，世界上總要有大部分呢種人先運行到。<br />\n唔係睇低佢地，而係有夢想嘅人總會改變到世界。如果太多嘅話，世界會亂。<br />\n呢個世界接納唔到幾多改變。你睇吓香港就知。"},{"pid":"b829367206fc19f1fb823ab42da9afc71a1b8cd3","tid":520784,"uid":98915,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T18:28:18.000Z","msg":"至於浪費人生，教人追逐夢想之前，倒不如教人認識自己先。<br />\n<br />\n夢想好遙不可及，講就好聽，最後係冇咩人會做。<br />\n<br />\n認識自己，客觀睇自己，唔好將自己嘅缺點收埋無視。<br />\n<br />\n有好多人會選擇性無視自己嘅缺點，然後又睇唔起其他人。<br />\n<br />\n揾日坐低，自己沉思自己係一個點嘅人，唔好為自己嘅缺點揾籍口。<br />\n<br />\n最最重要就係你要接受你只係一個庸人，一個普通人。<br />\n<br />\n你唔係世界嘅主角，你嘅才能一大堆人都有。呢個係最難克服嘅心理關口。<br />\n<br />\n當你認識咗自己，你就會為自己打算。你會無時無刻提醒自己係時候要改變得更好。<br />\n<br />\n見到同輩人得到成就唔會再揾籍口睇唔起人。你會欣賞佢嘅努力，然後更加鼓舞自己追上佢。<br />\n<br />\n俾自己一個好小嘅目標，例如做半個鐘運動，俾多啲成就感自己。慢慢你就發現唔知點解你會揾到夢想，揾到熱愛。"},{"pid":"e26d659e80a93aa851d1fd5ea6f38973eb117ec8","tid":520784,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中左兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多野你睇人好人睇你好 人地付出左好多努力先搵返成果 人地會羨慕你放假訓緊教玩緊輕輕鬆鬆生活</blockquote><br />\n懶散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c